Step 1: Grab any "low class" car off the street.

Step 2: Drive to a Garage.

Step 3: Go to "menu name" -> Vehicle -> Spawner -> Settings -> make sure "Upgraded" is ticked.

Step 4: Drive the stolen vehicle from the street into the garage.

Step 5: As soon as the drive-in cutscene starts, spam-spawn a car that you would like to keep.

Step 6: Once in garage get on it, and drive to LSC to buy insurance for it, in order to keep it after its been destroyed.

Step 7: Repeat for any car you wish to keep
